<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Aman Bhargava</title>


    <%- include('includes/head') %>

        <!-- Boostrap JS -->
        <script src="/scripts/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

        <!-- CSS -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/index.css">

</head>

<body>

    <!-- header -->
    <%- include('includes/header') %>

        <div id="backdrop"></div>
        <!-- main -->
        <main>

            <div class="animation-area ">
                <ul class="box-area">
                    <li>node.js</li>
                    <li></li>
                    <li>CSS</li>
                    <li>express.js</li>
                    <li></li>
                    <li>React.js</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="landingPageIntroSection">
                    <h1 class="greetingHeading">Hey, It's Me</h1>
                    <h1 class="nameHeading">Aman Bhargava</h1>
                    <p class="introBodyText">
                        An aspiring Software Developer
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- about -->
            <div class="about" id="about">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">

                        <div class="col-lg-6">
                            <div class="about_me_content">
                                <p class="heading">Hi! I'm Aman</p>
                                <p class="sub_heading">A Full Stack Developer based in Jaipur, India.</p>
                                <p class="text">
                                    I am delighted to welcome you to my personal website.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    I am a Computer Science graduate from SKIT, Jaipur, currently working at App Perfect
                                    Corp., Udaipur. Passionate about web
                                    development and DevOps, I created this platform to share my knowledge and connect
                                    with
                                    like-minded individuals. I hope you find it
                                    inspiring!

                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    During my college years, I embarked on a self-guided journey in web development,
                                    acquiring a strong foundation in
                                    various technologies such as HTML, CSS, Vanilla JS, and jQuery. I further
                                    honed my skills in both frontend and
                                    backend application development, gaining hands-on experience with frameworks,
                                    trending UI library and
                                    tools like Node.js, Express.js,
                                    React.js, PostgreSQL, and Firebase.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    In my professional role, I have expanded my expertise by exploring and working with
                                    modern technologies such as Go,
                                    Material React UI, and ORMs like Prisma. This exposure has cultivated a keen
                                    interest in DevOps, driving me to actively learn and apply concepts related to
                                    Docker, Kubernetes, and other tools that streamline software deployment and enhance
                                    scalability.

                                    <br>
                                    <br>

                                    As a full-stack developer, I am passionate about leveraging technology to create
                                    innovative solutions. From designing
                                    dynamic user interfaces to crafting efficient algorithms, I thrive on solving
                                    complex problems and bringing ideas to
                                    life with elegance and efficiency.
                                    <br>
                                    <br>
                                    I look forward to sharing my journey with you and exploring new opportunities in the
                                    world of webÂ development.
                                </p>
                                <div class="row">
                                    <a download="" class="downloadButton" href="/resume" target="_blank">
                                        <button id="resumeDownloadBtn">
                                            <span>
                                                Resume
                                            </span>
                                            <svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0"
                                                viewBox="0 0 512 512" height="1em" width="1em"
                                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                                <path
                                                    d="M216 0h80c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24v168h87.7c17.8 0 26.7 21.5 14.1 34.1L269.7 378.3c-7.5 7.5-19.8 7.5-27.3 0L90.1 226.1c-12.6-12.6-3.7-34.1 14.1-34.1H192V24c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24zm296 376v112c0 13.3-10.7 24-24 24H24c-13.3 0-24-10.7-24-24V376c0-13.3 10.7-24 24-24h146.7l49 49c20.1 20.1 52.5 20.1 72.6 0l49-49H488c13.3 0 24 10.7 24 24zm-124 88c0-11-9-20-20-20s-20 9-20 20 9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20zm64 0c0-11-9-20-20-20s-20 9-20 20 9 20 20 20 20-9 20-20z">
                                                </path>
                                            </svg>
                                        </button>
                                    </a>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-6 ">
                            <div class="my_image_div">
                                <img src="/images/basketball.jpg" class="img-fluid my_image" alt="My image">
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- projects -->
            <div class="project_div" id="project_div">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
                        <h1>Project's</h1>

                        <% for (project of projectArray){ %>
                            <div class="project_cards_div col-md-6 col-lg-3">
                                <a href="/project/<%= project.projectName %>" target="_self" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                                    <div class="project_cards">
                                        <img src="<%= project.projectImageUrl %>" alt="<%= project.projectName %>"
                                            class="img-fluid">
                                        <p>
                                            <%= project.projectName %> <i class="fas fa-angle-right"></i>
                                        </p>
                                    </div>
                                </a>
                            </div>
                            <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row" id="projectsRegsiterDiv">
                        Want to see more? Why not join our community, click here to join
                        <button type="button" id="projectsRegsiterBtn">
                            Register &nbsp; <i class="far fa-hand-pointer"></i>
                        </button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="registerModal">

                <div class="modalbody">

                    <p class="modalheading">Register</p>

                    <form action="/register" method="post">
                        <div>
                            <input type="text" name="firstName" id="firstName" required
                                placeholder="First Name (required)">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <input type="text" name="lastName" id="lastName" placeholder="Last Name">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <input type="email" name="emailID" id="emailID" required placeholder="Email (required)">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <input type="tel" name="contactNumber" id="contactNumber" placeholder="Contact Number">
                        </div>

                        <div>
                            <label for="DOB"><strong>D.O.B</strong></label>
                            <input type="date" name="DOB" id="DOB" placeholder="Date Of Birth">
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" id="registerSubmitForm">Submit</button>

                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>




            <!-- contact form -->
            <%- include('includes/contactForm') %>


        </main>

        <!-- script -->
        <script src="/scripts/index.js"></script>
        <script src="/scripts/ContactForm.js"></script>
</body>

</html>